About
About Western Audio-Video
For over thirty years, Western  Audio-Video has been delivering cutting edge services to Bay Area Homeowners  and Businesses. We have a track record rivaled by few in the industry and  continue to deliver professional installations, both large and small.
You will benefit from our knowledge  and experience. We have aligned ourselves with some of the industry’s best  brands, offer proven solutions, and keep our employees up to date through  constant training.
We are members of the Custom  Electronics and Design Association (CEDIA) and affiliates of the Imaging  Science Foundation (ISF) ISF. Both are highly regarded industry associations dedicated  to furthering the professionalism of their members.
We are a  California C-7 State Licensed Contractor with all the prerequisite insurance  and the financial capability to handle your project. 
California contractors license #740364

 


