Our Work
Videophile Home











This home features the newest in integration technology, and automation programming. 
Designed and built for the enjoyment of movies, TV,  and sports, this system focuses on video display. A large centralized equipment  center removes the clutter of electronics from 9 individually served rooms.  Standardized control makes them all operate in the same way, with identical  remote controls. Video is delivered to a variety of flat panel displays  including multiple LCD’s and one specialized outdoor plasma TV. The home  theater features a 65” plasma TV for casual viewing, and an overlaid 110”  videophile projection system which lowers out of the ceiling on demand, and  hides away when not in use. Theater quality sound is delivered by a flush7.2  channel surround system while maintaining the aesthetic appeal of the room.
Features / Technologies:

110” projection cinema, laid over 65”  Plasma
Outdoor entertainment area featuring  weatherproof plasma TV
Automated theater control
Multi-zone indoor/outdoor music
High speed home data network
Structured wiring package
Advanced multi-line telephone system



Services Included

 Home Cinema
 Multi-Room Audio
 Automation Control
 Data Networking
 Structured Wiring
 Advanced Telephone System






 


